title: PatD DISCOGRAPHY INCLUDES EVERYTHING
description:
*****************************Panic At The Disco*********************************
********************************Discography*************************************

#####Notes#####
Many albums were released as vinyls and there were different versions of songs on these album.  I have included these.  I also included the bonus tracks on the two 'studio albums' that were only on the Japanese releases.

The albums that had many artists on I only included the PatD songs.

All songs are tagged with 'PatD' as a contributing artist so that you can play everything with only selecting one artist.  Easy for iPods and such.

The 'String Tributes' are not PatD, they are various artists doing the 'studio albums' in a string quartet.

The album 'Live' is NOT an Album they released, it is simply a collection of all their live covers that weren't on other albums that I made.

Not all albums were 'big' releases so it's hard to find info on them.

Some of these albums were distributed ONLY to radio stations.

I tagged all the songs with ID3 tags AND PUT LYRICS in for iTunes/iPods.

I have also included album arts for everything.

I am still missing rare recordings of Iwsnt and bgtwt, and the radio edit for nita and Iwsnt, but I should get them soon.

Also I couldn't find the live version of Intermission for 'Live In Denver' so I subbed the album version.  If you have it let me know.
##########
